TITLE: SIGN UP JUMIA
DESCRIPTION: As a user, i want to be able to sign-up into my account on Jumia so i will be able to make orders without restriction.

Acceptance Criteria;
User should be able to launch Url www.jumia.com.ng
User should be able to view the account button on the homepage on jumia.com.ng
User should be able to click and be directed to Create an account.
User should be able to fill and input a valid email address and password
User should be able to add alphanumeric characters, numbers, signs in their respective fields
User should be required to pick a specific gender while creating an account.
User should be able to click the “create account button” to create an account using a valid email address, phone number and password and be directed to the homepage.


